[The change in policy and concern must be due to a mutual resolution of the
trade barriers between the countries involved. Previously, they were
concerned because the avian influenza had traversed the species barrier
into humans in China. If this outbreak is contained in small flocks and
does not reach the commercial flocks, perhaps the risk is less than it was
in China. Â­ Mod.TG
